      <title>伊朗袭击后油价下跌，市场风险溢价下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-after-iran-attack-market-draws-down-risk-premium-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一交易期间，油价下跌，因周六晚间伊朗袭击以色列后市场参与者回落风险溢价，以色列政府称此次袭击造成的损失有限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-after-iran-attack-market-draws-down-risk-premium-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 01:07:43 GMT</pubDate>
