    <item>
      <title>日本机械订单大幅增长或缓解内需担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-machinery-orders-rise-sharply-may-ease-concerns-about-domestic-demand-2024-04-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管当局担心日元贬值及其对生活成本的影响，但日本关键资本支出指标在 2 月份出现了一年来的最大涨幅，较上个月的下降大幅反弹，这是国内需求的一个可喜迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-machinery-orders-rise-sharply-may-ease-concerns-about-domestic-demand-2024-04-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 00:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
